\section{Language Keyword Reference}

Table~\ref{tab:all_keywords} provides a comprehensive reference of keywords in Al-Marjaa version 3.2.0.

\begin{table}[h]
\centering
\caption{Complete Keyword Reference}
\label{tab:all_keywords}
\small
\begin{tabular}{@{}llll@{}}
\toprule
